						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Hanumān temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 15th century.</p>						

						<p>This is dated the cyclic year Śrīmukha, Māgha śu. 1. The details of date cannot be verified. It records the gift of a village to the <hi rend="italic">Dombas.</hi> The epigraph is damaged.</p>						

